FBIS4-41046 "drsov120_i_94005" FBIS-SOV-94-120 Daily Report 21 Jun 1994 CENTRAL ASIA Kazakhstan Mongolian Ambassador Visits Balkhash, Discusses Settlers Mongolian Ambassador Visits Balkhash, Discusses Settlers LD2106132194 Almaty Kazakh Radio Network in Kazakh 0800 GMT 21 Jun 94 LD2106132194 Almaty Kazakh Radio Network Kazakh BFN [Text] Mongolian Ambassador to Kazakhstan Erdeniyn Byambajab arrived in Balkhash yesterday. Today he had a meeting with Vladimir Popovich, the head of the Balkhash city administration, leaders of local enterprises, and representatives of public organizations. Earlier he had a meeting with staff of the Balkhash [word indistinct]. The purpose of his visit is to familiarize himself with living and working conditions of Kazakh settlers from Mongolia.
